      "del:identifier": "delidata_argument_8b8f8303-4dfd-4e45-aa14-94b34ec9a7fe",
      "del:text": "Hi"
    },
    {
      "@type": "del:Argument",
      "del:identifier": "delidata_argument_6e852a02-c60a-485b-8f5c-bb546020fde0",
      "del:text": "'I thought we''d have to turn over the <CARD> \" card \"'"
    },
    {
      "@type": "del:Argument",
      "del:identifier": "delidata_argument_3ae416cc-8f56-48ca-b2fa-5bff8f31b965",
      "del:text": "Hi"
    },
    {
      "@type": "del:Argument",
      "del:identifier": "delidata_argument_632d4ca8-a904-4bb8-9cba-75409cfd9a89",
      "del:text": "'Me too , because it''s a vowel'"
    },
    {
      "@type": "del:Argument",
      "del:identifier": "delidata_argument_e0b129bb-bd3e-48e9-aa70-860395d9e79a",
      "del:text": "And <CARD> . Since it is an even number ."
    },
    {
      "@type": "del:Argument",
      "del:identifier": "delidata_argument_0a2f21cb-0d28-4bbc-9339-5201d28f8e4a",
      "del:text": "I also selected <CARD> \" since it is even . \""
    },
    {
      "@type": "del:Argument",
      "del:identifier": "delidata_argument_d819dd02-157a-48b2-8d72-e07619f750bc",
      "del:text": "Flipping each should test the rule ."
    },
    {
      "@type": "del:Argument",
      "del:identifier": "delidata_argument_25c7e140-f634-43dc-bf00-6939c6c49e59",
      "del:text": "'Well flipping <CARD> wouldn''t , would it ?'"
    },
    {
      "@type": "del:Argument",
      "del:identifier": "delidata_argument_fdb5a57e-9946-4fc4-9ee6-29760a73e58b",
      "del:text": "The rule pertains only to even numbers and vowels , right ?"
    },
    {
      "@type": "del:Argument",
      "del:identifier": "delidata_argument_6ac68a6f-f3bf-4ce2-8f82-5b8f50812d99",
      "del:text": "I guess we could flip <CARD> and if it has an even number , we know the rule is false ."
    },
    {
      "@type": "del:Argument",
      "del:identifier": "delidata_argument_ffed64df-a894-448f-ab82-346899c7cdec",
      "del:text": "'but it wouldn''t prove the rule true either'"
    },
    {
      "@type": "del:Argument",
      "del:identifier": "delidata_argument_2957b6bb-a420-4a0e-a5ee-13fb4e25772c",
      "del:text": "TRUE"
    },
    {
      "@type": "del:Argument",
      "del:identifier": "delidata_argument_60b4aba9-1097-4252-bfd9-2c0857829e2c",
      "del:text": "'I guess it''s just <CARD> and <CARD>'"
    },
    {
      "@type": "del:Argument",
      "del:identifier": "delidata_argument_afb4989f-3e84-4c1c-b557-2ec7b4645009",
      "del:text": "'I think it''s <CARD> because the rule is , All cards with vowels \"'"
    },
    {
      "@type": "del:Argument",
      "del:identifier": "delidata_argument_50711ad2-5c2e-48b5-ba2d-b886f2db0fba",
      "del:text": "I am sticking to <CARD> and <CARD> as well ."
    },
    {
      "@type": "del:Argument",
      "del:identifier": "delidata_argument_6c01a6c9-6481-440b-a92c-16ff5a07a45a",
      "del:text": "OK ... i will defer to the majority"
    },
    {
      "@type": "del:Argument",
      "del:identifier": "delidata_argument_4135886a-61d2-4ddc-88b0-8b4608c63a82",
      "del:text": "We are verifying the rule , not falsifying it ."
    },
    {
      "@type": "del:Argument",
      "del:identifier": "delidata_argument_caf306ac-255d-4b26-9da7-d7f17ed09057",
      "del:text": "I am not good at this stuff"
    },
    {
      "@type": "del:Argument",
      "del:identifier": "delidata_argument_26abbbcd-785c-4b80-a0c7-83eca4269797",
      "del:text": "How long do we have to wait ?"
    },
    {
      "@type": "del:Argument",
      "del:identifier": "delidata_argument_6fa9151e-1a66-449e-bebd-7aaf3c5219bb",
      "del:text": "2 minutes and 30 seconds"
    },
    {
      "@type": "del:Argument",
      "del:identifier": "delidata_argument_6a877c9c-bedc-444c-b3a1-70b668f35a09",
      "del:text": "Theres a timer on the top left hand of my screen"
    },
    {
      "@type": "del:Argument",
      "del:identifier": "delidata_argument_625099c4-7fb1-483f-acd6-e062fbce54a0",
      "del:text": "gotcha ... just saw that"
    },
    {
      "@type": "del:Argument",
      "del:identifier": "delidata_argument_4dfa3d95-1f58-4c78-ab13-9cd62d7f97b7",
      "del:text": "'I don''t think flipping <CARD> verifies the rule'"
    },
    {
      "@type": "del:Argument",
      "del:identifier": "delidata_argument_3d3daf1f-cc3f-49a8-ac72-df174ba7b8f8",
      "del:text": "Thanks <MENTION> and <MENTION> !"
    },
    {
      "@type": "del:Argument",
      "del:identifier": "delidata_argument_9419ae40-fe6f-4ef8-8a07-f454a89248a2",
      "del:text": "How come ?"
    },
    {
      "@type": "del:Argument",
      "del:identifier": "delidata_argument_e67a7aa7-590e-4482-b1fa-49729e51e551",
      "del:text": "Oh . I see now ."
    },
    {
      "@type": "del:Argument",
      "del:identifier": "delidata_argument_622eea1d-1a9f-4b54-8d0c-95394af3b6ec",
      "del:text": "'Because if the other side is a consonant , it doesn''t change the fact that all cards with vowels on one side have an even number'"
    },
    {
      "@type": "del:Argument",
      "del:identifier": "delidata_argument_67770571-9432-45c6-ac26-b8b65fafe460",
      "del:text": "Good catch !"
    },
    {
      "@type": "del:Argument",
      "del:identifier": "delidata_argument_982e0c61-abd3-482c-b534-b32e129f9263",
      "del:text": "'I really don''t know . The more I think about it the more it confuses me'"
    },
    {
      "@type": "del:Argument",
      "del:identifier": "delidata_argument_aa7620c8-0ed0-4c77-bb26-9e7c7b866b13",
      "del:text": "'So we''re out of time ?'"
    }
  ]
